### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health


### Get all vehicles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/vehicles


### Create vehicle
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plateNumber": "ABC123",
  "brand": "Toyota",
  "model": "Hilux",
  "year": 2024,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}